{"id": "1295797994247028816", "channel_id": "1295797994247028816", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168855337609199728", "author_name": "anachico", "author_bot": false, "content": "因为亿些事情耽搁了一阵，随后被一堆怪物们淹没<:flop:1236937860922343466> \n双子因为复杂度略高可能会有部分误差，但4个阶段实在是不想再复盘了，谨慎参考<:Coffee:1240919421791375380> \n\n本期收录截止至2024年10月16日，且为了方便理解对部分细节进行了适当修改，实际效果请以游戏内为准！\nUID：100012579", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T17:18:36.591000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295797994980901016", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1637660, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295797994247028816/1295797994980901016/1.jpg?ex=69cc01ec&is=69cab06c&hm=3783d643977ab09718e70a828e7412805395e5fab99cae0bb18af01b3b40fff2&"}, {"id": "1295797995790663680", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1496241, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295797994247028816/1295797995790663680/2.jpg?ex=69cc01ec&is=69cab06c&hm=336059894c9a42f52724c688a6e42e0763de72d1e9dd415ab23a2bc5a999c0ba&"}, {"id": "1295797996713152572", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2021885, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295797994247028816/1295797996713152572/3.jpg?ex=69cc01ed&is=69cab06d&hm=6df3b7b71464c3ef91197f1de8bf7161dbd5e141daa9abc10e388b13daeb4ae1&"}, {"id": "1295797997359206450", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2523246, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295797994247028816/1295797997359206450/4.jpg?ex=69cc01ed&is=69cab06d&hm=71b7dc17b67140b4f7a5e88e5e647a8d583e4c7b2a673c9b3ea42e3417f21a76&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295797994247028816", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【敌方意图收录】第8章下篇新增单位一览", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1295798959763095649", "channel_id": "1287040439827955783", "type": 19, "author_id": "1168855337609199728", "author_name": "anachico", "author_bot": false, "content": "手上比较完整的资料只有内测时期的记录（截止第五章），而且是纯文字版的，公测之后乱七八糟的改动很多可能不太有参考价值<:stoppage:1236938521365839872> 不过第六章之后大部分新怪出来后我都有做长图发在dc，需要的话可以搜索一下？", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T17:22:26.788000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["884607881360572476"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1291644631469264910", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1287040439827955783", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【敌方意图收录】第8章中篇新增单位一览", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1295724676072345661", "channel_id": "1295724676072345661", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，這次為大家帶來的是血鏈·希洛支線地圖。\n\n本次活動玩法及特殊造物效果詳見：https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1295723420134412369\n\n注意：\n\n紅地板「血污之池」：經過後消失，可選 失去全部狂氣並刪除1張症狀卡 / 回復血量並被塞2張症狀卡。", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:27:16.176000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295724677527765045", "filename": "low.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1519783, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295724676072345661/1295724677527765045/low.jpg?ex=69cbbda4&is=69ca6c24&hm=0d9463b65a249972f0cce4c3582c4e8f997c0623f3e90d98489555b4f6e71060&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295724676072345661", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特遣紀錄「艾爾沃斯的歸人」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1295724745064583219", "channel_id": "1295724676072345661", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "P.S.劇情關和活動地圖不一樣！劇情關直接可以戰鬥，活動關是迷霧結節！ ！", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:27:32.625000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295724744544485417", "filename": "MEITU_20241015_162932675.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2778429, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295724676072345661/1295724744544485417/MEITU_20241015_162932675.jpg?ex=69cbbdb4&is=69ca6c34&hm=97dfc062e6c007199aa26e9e645a8f78bb0c76174fad0cf5e5b2949e52bd2548&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295724676072345661", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特遣紀錄「艾爾沃斯的歸人」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1295723420134412369", "channel_id": "1295723420134412369", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，本期為大家帶來的是血鏈·希洛的限時活動地圖。\n\n限時活動入口，在主界面左下角「雪山消融之時」-「野獸野心」處進入。\n\n**關卡地圖**\n經過紫地板「惡沼」時，會扣除血量上限的約5%，也就是固定值。當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判定為致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n\n紅地板「血污之池」：經過後消失，可選 失去全部狂氣並刪除1張症狀卡 / 回復血量並被塞2張症狀卡。", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:22:16.737000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295723423481200650", "filename": "LOW.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3500163, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295723420134412369/1295723423481200650/LOW.jpg?ex=69cbbc79&is=69ca6af9&hm=e8d613ca44dd4ee68631006d030ab8bca9c02446c51b694be90e61dd81d0cd09&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295723420134412369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限時活動「野獸雄心」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1295723803233488966", "channel_id": "1295723420134412369", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "**共鳴與玩法**\n本共鳴有左右兩條路線，左：依科考團人數增益；右：全增益。\n\n根據預設開啟的共鳴，探索開始時會獲得造物「科考團」，你需要帶領科考團安全撤離！", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:23:48.075000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1295723802973569054", "filename": "ca2e432fecffd070.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 960447, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295723420134412369/1295723802973569054/ca2e432fecffd070.jpg?ex=69cbbcd4&is=69ca6b54&hm=96ad9e32e8db78f8bf2959ef1cde97a2a14ab408465812266492ec4080a80985&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295723420134412369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限時活動「野獸雄心」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1295723905390088223", "channel_id": "1295723420134412369", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "每場比賽都會獲得5張猜疑（人數0除外），此卡牌打出後有4種效果（共鳴左1野獸項圈後獲得【全力配合】）：", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:24:12.431000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1295723905474105385", "filename": "35de02e6000e95af.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1467912, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295723420134412369/1295723905474105385/35de02e6000e95af.png?ex=69cbbcec&is=69ca6b6c&hm=3af8ded1fde73d74f10c4bfc9c5bac21ad7f94d10ea7ddc33ac29b5470f8bee4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295723420134412369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限時活動「野獸雄心」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1295723964143767672", "channel_id": "1295723420134412369", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "這是科考團本身的效果。當你帶領科考團安全撤離時，也會根據科考團人數有所增益。", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:24:26.439000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295723420134412369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限時活動「野獸雄心」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
