{"id": "1295724056758452236", "channel_id": "1295723420134412369", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "最後到達「安全撤離點」時，會移除造物「科考團」，並根據剩餘科考團人數獲得「救援勳章」，撤離人數越多「救援勳章」越強大！\n\n人性光輝每回合都有1張，點滿共鳴時，每回合都給2張；無人生還時，獨行者之徽的力量翻倍。", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:24:48.520000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295723420134412369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限時活動「野獸雄心」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1295724119538667642", "channel_id": "1295723420134412369", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-10-15T12:25:03.488000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1295724119215833098", "filename": "690e5320efc67a16.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 5854670, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295723420134412369/1295724119215833098/690e5320efc67a16.jpg?ex=69cbbd1f&is=69ca6b9f&hm=134290e46c8337d2d29ec9ee83ccb336a8168a204e742c70f522d2b95336ae32&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295723420134412369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限時活動「野獸雄心」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
